      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty is in incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I've truly babied this car since day one, keeping it spotless and always tucked away in the garage. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that feels basically brand new without the dealership headache, you\u2019ve found it. I'd love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed!",
