    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S is a superlative example of the 996.2 generation, featuring the iconic wide-body silhouette and an advanced all-wheel-drive system utilizing a viscous multi-plate clutch. The 3.6L naturally aspirated flat-six engine delivers seamless power through VarioCam Plus technology, paired with a precise 6-speed manual transaxle. Mechanical provenance is impeccable: the IMS bearing has been proactively addressed, and a recent borescope inspection confirms pristine cylinder walls. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, supported by four-piston monoblock calipers and cross-drilled rotors that provide exceptional thermal management. Every gasket is dry, and the suspension bushings remain compliant yet firm, offering the direct steering feedback characteristic of this analog era. This is an investment-grade specimen for the collector who prioritizes mechanical purity and performance telemetry.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
