      "description": "Hey there! You've absolutely got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s honestly like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it shows. No scratches, a spotless interior, and it drives like a dream. It\u2019s been my pride and joy, but it\u2019s ready for a new home where it\u2019ll be just as loved. If you're looking for that brand-new feel without the brand-new sticker price, this is the one! Drop me a message if you want to take it for a spin!",
